tafsir[15]{c,v,t}:
  55,70,"In these four gardens there are women with good characters and beautiful faces."
  55,72,"Houris covered in tents as protection for them."
  55,74,"Before their husbands no man or jinn has come close to them."
  56,1,"When the inevitable rising will occur."
  56,2,"There will be no soul that denies it like how it used to deny in the world."
  56,4,"When the earth is shaken violently."
  56,5,"And the mountains are completely crushed."
  56,6,"Due to this crushing they will become scattered dust."
  56,7,"You will be in three categories on that day."
  56,10,"Those who were foremost in doing good deeds in the world they will be foremost in the afterlife to enter Paradise."
  56,11,"They are the ones who will be brought close to Allah."
  56,13,"A group from this nation and from previous nation."
  56,14,"A few people at the end of time will be the foremost ones that are brought close."
  56,15,"On couches woven with gold."
  56,16,"Reclining on these couches facing one another and no one will look at the back of another."